      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At least two independent test conditions (e.g., load rate, temperature) or two independent laboratories. Required gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load rate (5 mm/min) and single ambient temperature (23±2°C) per ASTM F1717. Although two laboratories participated, the test protocol was identical in both facilities, providing no variation in test conditions. This factor is assessed at gradation 1 — below the required level of 2. This gap is acknowledged and does not invalidate the overall assessment given that all other factors meet or exceed required levels."
    },
